reviews.name: Richard M.
reviews.review: I reserved a space at the Opera Plaza Garage on ParkMe.com.  We had opera tickets the same day as Gay Pride, and were taking a handicapped person with us so we had to drive in.  I was worried that the lot would be full, or that they wouldn't know about the reservation.  I called the lot's phone number - someone answered and said "no problems".  Indeed, I drove in, left the car and picked it up after the opera, no problems .

I don't think I will park here again.
